<recipe>
	<name>Tangy Post-Cooked Shrimp with Parsley or Chives</name>
	<notes>I cant say I much like where this recipe ultimately headed and I have no idea why I liked it so much when I printed it out.  Cold shrimp salad sounds not like up my alley:  I like my cold shrimp with cocktail sauce, thanks.

Still, it -was- in the collection.</notes>
